title: How Do You Make Warwick's Q Go Behind People?
body: I have a Lenovo Calliope USB Keyboard. I use Quick Cast.  I have tried holding down the Q key all the time while left clicking. I have tried holding Q then releasing and pressing it again immediately. I have tried tapping Q twice. I do not understand how it works. Please help. Thanks in advance. Warwick either does nothing or just does the little leap instead.

replies.body:
keeping Q pressed should do the trick.
idk why its not working for you though.
found this video if it helps.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xYeWlcoOFY4

What purpose does the left clicking serve?

Point at the enemy champion, press and hold Q.
